Linked Discourses 12
8. Ascetics and Brahmins
72–81. A Set of Ten on Rebirth, Etc.
# NOTE: Quote marks? Seriously?
At Sāvatthī.
“… they don’t understand rebirth …
continued existence …
grasping …
craving …
feeling …
contact …
the six sense fields …
name and form …
consciousness …
choices …
… they understand …”










# NOTE: This all reads like the end of the samyutta.

